Text:
to AONE-88  - what's the problem man? 
 this shit should be seen, and it's now got a worldwide audience.
the whole point is to get your shit out there for people to see, especially other writers in the scene...i mean, really, how many people are going to get to bucharest and have a chance to see this?
embrace the p2p revolution, my friend.
like the graffiti movement, it's unstoppable.
peace.
